50|$|Rubin Central Design <b>Bureau's</b> <b>chief</b> {{designer}} <b>for</b> the Amur-1650 and -950 is Yuri Kormilitsyn. As {{the further}} development of ideas already implemented in Kilo-class submarines, Amur-class boats are single-hulled, with minimal displacement, allowing for reduced noise signature and improved propulsion quality. A totally new main electric engine using permanent magnets is in development/construction and projected to give high energy conversion efficiency even at low cruise speeds.|$|R
